# Commit Message Template for ElanRegistry
# 
# Format: TYPE: Brief description (Issue #XXX)
#
# Types: FIX, FEATURE, ENHANCEMENT, SECURITY, REFACTOR, DOCS, TEST, VERSION
#
# Examples:
# FIX: reCAPTCHA bypass vulnerability in login process (Issue #XXX)
# FEATURE: Add dark mode toggle to user settings (Issue #XXX)  
# ENHANCEMENT: Improve car search performance with database indexing (Issue #XXX)
# VERSION: Bump to v2.3.5 - Security fixes and performance improvements
#
# ✅ CHECKLIST (delete lines that don't apply):
# [ ] Updated VERSION file (required for code changes to main branch)
# [ ] Created matching git tag (recommended for releases)
# [ ] Updated relevant documentation
# [ ] Added/updated tests for new functionality
# [ ] Verified no breaking changes
# [ ] Security review completed (for security-related changes)
#
# 🤖 This commit will include the standard Claude Code footer automatically